=== Sample Size and Power

With n=50 participants and 3 imaging timepoints per subject:
    - 80% power to detect Spearman $rho$=0.35 between TSPO-PET and PEM recovery time at $alpha$=0.05
    - Sufficient for subgroup analyses by PEM trajectory
    - Adequate for exploratory regional analyses


